# Faz 10: Dashboard + Error Pages + Polish

## Goal

S-DASHBOARD permission-gated widget'lar (parallel lazy load, widget isolation). InternalLayout finalizasyon: sidebar tüm menüler PermissionGate, topbar NotificationBell + user menu + breadcrumb. Error pages S-FORBIDDEN, S-NOT-FOUND, S-ERROR (prod'da stack yok). S-SESSION-EXPIRED modal → re-login. KVKK consent blocking modal (ESC/outside click/X disabled). Loading/empty/error state tutarlılığı.

Detay: `Docs/10_IMPLEMENTATION_ROADMAP.md` §Faz 10.

**Bağımlılık:** Faz 5–9 core screens; Faz 9 KVKK publish API; Faz 8 NotificationBell.

