### İterasyon 1 — Dashboard Backend

**Hedef:** Aggregate metadata API; plaintext etik içerik yok; session list + revoke.

**Yapılacaklar:**

1. `GET /api/v1/dashboard/summary` — counts only: open cases, closed, SLA breaches, pending tasks
2. Şirket/kategori dağılımı — metadata aggregation (no report_text)
3. `GET /api/v1/auth/sessions`, `DELETE /api/v1/auth/sessions/:id` — own sessions revoke
4. `@RequirePolicy`; PolicyScope on aggregates
5. Integration test: response body grep — incident_description/report_text absent

**Minimum bağlam:**

- `Docs/03_API_CONTRACTS.md` §8.14 Dashboard
- `Docs/07_SECURITY_IMPLEMENTATION.md` — dashboard no content leak
- `.cursor/rules/12-authorization-policy.mdc`

**Bu iterasyonda yok:** Frontend widgets, error pages.

**Stop:** [ ] No plaintext ethical content in summary; [ ] session revoke works. PR/onay → İterasyon 2.

