## Constraints

### Use

- Widget-level parallel fetch + isolation
- Permission-gated widgets
- Prod error pages — no stack trace
- Session expired interceptor → modal
- KVKK modal truly blocking
- Dashboard summary — metadata only

### Avoid

- Single monolithic dashboard query
- Stack trace in prod S-ERROR
- Dismissible KVKK modal
- Widget cascade fail (one fail kills page)
- Ethical content in dashboard API

