### Human Gate

- [ ] Widget isolation verified
- [ ] Prod no stack trace
- [ ] PR squash merge → `main`

## Explicit Don'ts

- Monolithic dashboard query
- Stack trace prod error pages
- Dismissible KVKK consent
- Dashboard ethical plaintext
- New feature scope in polish phase
- `main`'e direct push

